𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗔𝗺𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗰𝗮𝗻 𝗗𝗿𝗲𝗮𝗺 𝗶𝘀 𝗺𝗼𝗿𝗲 𝗮𝗹𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝘁𝗵𝗮𝗻 𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗿…⁣
⁣
17 years ago to this day my family & I entered the greatest country on earth…⁣
⁣
The United States Of America 🇺🇸 ⁣
⁣
My family and I had no choice but to leave as we were persecuted Christian. ⁣
⁣
Prior to immigrating to the USA my family & I had the privilege of helping the US military keep the power⚡️ on in the chow halls⁣
⁣
Our lives were at risk on a daily basis so we made took the long trip west in 2006🇺🇸⁣
⁣
Nobody ever said that you were going to have to start from scratch! ⁣
⁣
So here we go…. ⁣
⁣
FLAT BROKE IN THE TRENCHES. ⁣
⁣
I became a worker for hire. ⁣
⁣
I Worked as a Laundry mat associate (went to Zero-Hour School) to gain an extra hour of work
⁣
I worked as an AC tech assistant in Arizona where the heat is 120+ degrees 🥵⁣
⁣
I then worked as a plumber mostly consisting of fixing leaks in peoples homes.⁣
⁣
I would also Door knock houses that were on the golf course ⛳️ to offer my service as a metal fence rust scraper & painter⁣
⁣
I also Worked with the US military for 3.5 years as a contracted trainer (role player) in a series of monthly training called “Rotation” where the troops would train by living in a lookalike environment to help them face real wartime experiences. ⁣
⁣
This training meant the difference between troops surviving & coming back home from the war & not making it back to their families.⁣
Saving lives is a feeling that cannot be described⁣
⁣
I decided to open up a small car dealership with 7 cars on the lot.⁣
⁣
That same year I Became a US citizen.⁣
⁣
What a blessing…⁣
⁣
Fast forward to today…⁣
⁣
Today I own & operate multiple companies (that employ 100s of people and impact 1000s of lives) from real estste investing to software & data companies to a beautiful brand that contributes & helps thousands of lives achieve financial freedom around a faith based community ❤️🚀⁣
⁣
You see, all you have to do is get off your as* & take charge of your future, no one owes you anything and your destiny is in your hands!⁣
⁣
𝗚𝗢𝗗, 𝗙𝗔𝗠𝗜𝗟𝗬, 𝗛𝗨𝗦𝗧𝗟𝗘⁣
⁣
Sending you nothing but love today on this beautiful Saturday afternoon!⁣
⁣
God bless🙏🏼
